                            <comment id="13470745" author="yuzhihong@gmail.com" created="Fri, 5 Oct 2012 22:41:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;To do this, we need to specify the path to GC log:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
-Xloggc:/apache/hbase/logs/gc-hbase.log
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Should a variable, such as HBASE_GC_LOG_PATH, be introduced so that user can specify the location ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13470750" author="stack" created="Fri, 5 Oct 2012 22:45:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We have a logging dir define already.  We&apos;ll reuse that.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
